âœ¨ Summary (Day 11):

Duplicates = repeated values in a list.

Easy trick â†’ Convert to Set and compare size with original list.

Useful in orders ðŸ§¾, shopping carts ðŸ›’, weekly sales ðŸ“ˆ, or student IDs ðŸŽ“.



